{"tid":446301,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(PS4) Fifa18 ProClub VPL隊 招LCB , RCB (車仔踢法)","createTime":"2017-10-24T07:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T13:15:12.000Z","uid":10175,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66ae8751378d1d888c38c43a4936636c517fb79f","tid":446301,"uid":10175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"巳參加今季<span style=\"color: gold;\">VPL比賽</span>, 中前場人才濟濟，中堅也有主力球員坐鎮，只欠2名 後衛球員 <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">LCB RCB</span> (打三中堅陣）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n球會陣式：343 (3-4-2-1)，以三中堅為球隊基本陣型，小組短傳為主，不會胡亂吊高波及長傳。這個陣式最重要是翼衛，<br />\n八字真言：<span style=\"color: violet;\">進攻拉闊，防守收窄</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本球會現正招收以下位置<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">LCB/RCB</span> 左中堅/右中堅<br />\n主要功能：與CB配合聯防，進攻時可拉闊兩邊引開對手，再直線地波/高波放上前場兩翼位置。<br />\n防守時可與防中/正中堅 聯合迫搶 也可以互補防線空位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n球會常上線球員有9人, 希望招收一些常上線, 不會經常轉隊踢,會用咪,性格開朗之隊友.<br />\n球會一星期<span style=\"color: teal;\">最少五天以上會上線</span>, 時間為晚上<span style=\"color: teal;\">10:00~2:00(大約)</span>,星期六日及假期會看球隊上線人數再決定.<br />\n<br />\n如有興趣者可 TG: <span style=\"color: gold;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/Cart_Noodle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCart_Noodle&d=HdUXrYEkG2fOkZ1wUI3%2FRARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e6bc13f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/Cart_Noodle</a></span><br />\n<br />\n可寫下要求位置及留下psn方便本人加你試腳.<br />\n<br />\n謝謝."},{"pid":"8b08c16d3db65801f64a970da788158a0232c66e","tid":446301,"uid":10175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:49:19.000Z","msg":"推~~~~"},{"pid":"2ba07261bd88a6219f34c4a468fd5b6691278dbd","tid":446301,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f345a7fac57819921f81ddedebcc6f204eff3c","tid":446301,"uid":10175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"推～～"},{"pid":"3021